Package au.org.massive.strudel_web

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsyncTasks
    A servlet listener to keep a thread pool active during the life of the application
    KeyService
    Provides key pair generation and certificate signing services
    LoginController
    The login controller kicks off the OAuth2 auth flow and notifies the client when auth is complete.
    OAuthService
    Provides methods for the OAuth2 auth flow
    RegexHelper
    Some regex helper utilities
    Session
    An abstraction from the HttpSession object, mediating access to session attributes
    SessionManager
    A session listener that cleans up any leftovers when a session ends, and keeps track of all active sessions
    Settings
    Provides settings for the application.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoSuchSessionException
    Thrown if a Session object is requested but not found
    UnauthorizedException
    Thrown during the OAuth2 flow if the user is not authorised.
